about

A follow on from the 'Cereal Without Milk Are Crisps Sessions' this additional 16 sixteen tracks spans the abuse of noise as music theme. Each track has elements of what are considered artefacts of musicianship but twisted and skewed into a mash of noise collages, even though recorded live in one take and taking into account the many scales on offer within the musical universe.
